---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="Conferences">
  <div class="prose max-w-none">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Conference Presentations</h1>

    <p class="text-base mb-8">
      Attending conferences is one of the true highlights of being in science - for the ideas, the personal connections, and the travel. I pick them carefully and travel by train where possible. You can spot the trips where I chose the train over a plane with the
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 align-middle">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="inline text-accent"><path d="M8 3.1V7a4 4 0 0 0 8 0V3.1"/><path d="m9 15-1-1"/><path d="m15 15 1-1"/><path d="M9 19c-2.8 0-5-2.2-5-5v-4a8 8 0 0 1 16 0v4c0 2.8-2.2 5-5 5Z"/><path d="m8 19-2 3"/><path d="m16 19 2 3"/></svg>
        icon below.
      </span>
    </p>

    <!-- International conferences -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 border-b pb-2">International Conferences</h2>

    <div class="space-y-8 mb-10">

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">European Sleep Research Society (ESRS) Sleep Europe</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm pl-2">
          <li><span class="font-medium">2026</span> - Maastricht, the Netherlands - <span class="text-accent font-medium">Symposium co-chair, oral presentation, poster</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span><span class="font-medium">2024</span> - Seville, Spain - <span class="text-accent font-medium">Symposium chair, oral presentation</span></span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-accent shrink-0"><path d="M8 3.1V7a4 4 0 0 0 8 0V3.1"/><path d="m9 15-1-1"/><path d="m15 15 1-1"/><path d="M9 19c-2.8 0-5-2.2-5-5v-4a8 8 0 0 1 16 0v4c0 2.8-2.2 5-5 5Z"/><path d="m8 19-2 3"/><path d="m16 19 2 3"/></svg>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span><span class="font-medium">2023</span> - Fréjus, France (course) - <span class="text-accent font-medium">Poster, oral presentation</span></span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-accent shrink-0"><path d="M8 3.1V7a4 4 0 0 0 8 0V3.1"/><path d="m9 15-1-1"/><path d="m15 15 1-1"/><path d="M9 19c-2.8 0-5-2.2-5-5v-4a8 8 0 0 1 16 0v4c0 2.8-2.2 5-5 5Z"/><path d="m8 19-2 3"/><path d="m16 19 2 3"/></svg>
          </li>
          <li><span class="font-medium">2022</span> - Athens, Greece - <span class="text-accent font-medium">Poster</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Organization for Human Brain Mapping (OHBM)</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm pl-2">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span><span class="font-medium">2026</span> - Bordeaux, France - <span class="text-accent font-medium">Poster</span></span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-accent shrink-0"><path d="M8 3.1V7a4 4 0 0 0 8 0V3.1"/><path d="m9 15-1-1"/><path d="m15 15 1-1"/><path d="M9 19c-2.8 0-5-2.2-5-5v-4a8 8 0 0 1 16 0v4c0 2.8-2.2 5-5 5Z"/><path d="m8 19-2 3"/><path d="m16 19 2 3"/></svg>
          </li>
          <li><span class="font-medium">2025</span> - Brisbane, Australia - <span class="text-accent font-medium">Posters</span></li>
          <li><span class="font-medium">2023</span> - Montréal, Canada - <span class="text-accent font-medium">Poster</span></li>
          <li><span class="font-medium">2022</span> - Glasgow, United Kingdom (online) - <span class="text-accent font-medium">Poster</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Nordic Sleep Conference</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm pl-2">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span><span class="font-medium">2026</span> - Copenhagen, Denmark - <span class="text-accent font-medium">Symposium co-chair, oral presentation</span></span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-accent shrink-0"><path d="M8 3.1V7a4 4 0 0 0 8 0V3.1"/><path d="m9 15-1-1"/><path d="m15 15 1-1"/><path d="M9 19c-2.8 0-5-2.2-5-5v-4a8 8 0 0 1 16 0v4c0 2.8-2.2 5-5 5Z"/><path d="m8 19-2 3"/><path d="m16 19 2 3"/></svg>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">International REM Sleep Behaviour Disorder Study Group</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm pl-2">
          <li><span class="font-medium">2025</span> - Groningen, the Netherlands - <span class="text-accent font-medium">Poster</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">International Lewy Body Dementia Conference</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm pl-2">
          <li><span class="font-medium">2025</span> - Amsterdam, the Netherlands - <span class="text-accent font-medium">Poster</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">European Narcolepsy Days</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm pl-2">
          <li><span class="font-medium">2023</span> - Leiden, the Netherlands - <span class="text-accent font-medium">Poster</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Sleep, Cognition & Consciousness Winter Symposium</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm pl-2">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span><span class="font-medium">2023</span> - Werfenweng, Austria - <span class="text-accent font-medium">Poster</span></span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-accent shrink-0"><path d="M8 3.1V7a4 4 0 0 0 8 0V3.1"/><path d="m9 15-1-1"/><path d="m15 15 1-1"/><path d="M9 19c-2.8 0-5-2.2-5-5v-4a8 8 0 0 1 16 0v4c0 2.8-2.2 5-5 5Z"/><path d="m8 19-2 3"/><path d="m16 19 2 3"/></svg>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Neuroscience of Dreaming (course)</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm pl-2">
          <li><span class="font-medium">2024</span> - Nijmegen, the Netherlands</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- International one-day meetings -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 border-b pb-2">International One-Day Meetings</h2>

    <div class="space-y-8 mb-10">

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">ISMRM Benelux Annual Meeting</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm pl-2">
          <li><span class="font-medium">2025</span> - Hilversum, the Netherlands - <span class="text-accent font-medium">Poster</span></li>
          <li><span class="font-medium">2024</span> - Den Bosch, the Netherlands - <span class="text-accent font-medium">Oral presentation</span></li>
          <li><span class="font-medium">2023</span> - Brussels, Belgium - <span class="text-accent font-medium">Poster</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Symposium on Neuroimaging, Sleep, Lifestyle & Cognition</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm pl-2">
          <li><span class="font-medium">2025</span> - Montréal, Canada - <span class="text-accent font-medium">Poster</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- National conferences -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 border-b pb-2">National Conferences</h2>

    <div class="space-y-8 mb-10">

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">SLAAP (National Sleep Conference)</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm pl-2">
          <li><span class="font-medium">2025</span> - Eindhoven, the Netherlands - <span class="text-accent font-medium">Symposium chair, oral presentation</span></li>
          <li><span class="font-medium">2023</span> - Papendal, the Netherlands - <span class="text-accent font-medium">Symposium chair, oral presentation</span></li>
          <li><span class="font-medium">2021</span> - Online - <span class="text-accent font-medium">Poster</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- National one-day meetings -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 border-b pb-2">National One-Day Meetings</h2>
    <p class="text-sm">
      Regular attendance of Sleep Spring and Fall Symposia of the Dutch Society for Sleep-Wake Research (2021-2025),
      the Dutch Parkinson Scientists Congress (2022-2025), and the Amsterdam Neuroscience Annual Meeting (2022-2026).
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10">
      <a href="/cv" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm">Back to CV</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>
